Lenovo ideacentre Y710 Cube-15ISH
Intel® Core™ i7-6700 CPU @ 3.40GHz × 8
NVIDIA Corporation GP104 [GeForce GTX 1080]
Ubuntu 22.04.5 LTS
64-bit
16GiB System Memory: 2 x 8GiB DIMM DDR4 Synchronous 2133 MHz
2 x 128KiB L1 cache; 1MiB L2 cache; 8MiB L3 cache
Internal Solid State Drive (256GB TLC SATA 6Gbps)

/etc/default/zramswap
ALGO=lz4
PERCENT=300

zram compresses 48 GB into 16 GB in RAM, and thus it works fine to build 500,000,000 [Ar].
FIXME: the cotents in the /swapfile file are not compressed, and thus it crashes
  when building 700,000,000 [Ar] (> 20 GB cotents saved in /swapfile)

